entries.entry: We started working on Martins Aquarium. Nothing crazy so far.
Went over the Github workflow and practiced some ourselves. It's a little convoluted right now but the concept seems simple.
Learned how to input structural shortcuts for html in the terminal. I'll take it if it makes my life easier.
Continued working on the aquarium. Also, we reviewed some concepts we've been working on.
Friday is here again and I feel more confident in my abilites but am no where near feeling like I know what I'm doing.
